Executive Profile
Michael S. Samis  Director and Director of BancFirst, BancFirst CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships63$30,000
Background

		Mr. Michael S. Samis, also known as Mike, is a Co-Founder and Chairman of Energy Financial Solutions, LLC and Founder and Chairman of Energy Financial and Physical, LLC. Mr. Samis served as President and Chief Executive Officer of Macklanburg-Duncan Company from 1990 to 2000 and served as its Chairman. He served as Chief Executive Officer of M-D Building Products, Inc. Prior to M-D, he served as Vice-President for Hiawatha Oil Company, a large independent oil and gas ... exploration and production company in Oklahoma City. Mr. Samis has been Chairman of University Hospitals Authority and Trust since June 2000. He serves as Chairman of the University Hospital Authority, University Hospitals Trust and Joint Governing Committee for OU Medical Center. He served as Chairman and Member of The Board of M-D Building Products Inc. from 2000 to 2007. He has been Director of University Hospitals Authority and Trust since 1993. He has been a Director of BancFirst Corporation since May 23, 2014 and serves as Director of BancFirst. Mr. Samis served as Director of the Oklahoma City Branch of the Federal Reserve Bank of Kansas City from 1995 to 2001. He is the recipient of the 2002 Alumni Achievement Award from Casady School and the 2007 University of Oklahoma Regents’ Alumni Award. He serves on the boards of Oklahoma Medical Research Foundation, Dean A. McGee Eye Institute, Presbyterian Health Foundation, Oklahoma Health Center Foundation, OU Health Sciences Center and Committee of 100. He remains active in Oklahoma City community affairs, having served on numerous community and charitable boards. He received a Bachelor’s Degree from the University of Oklahoma in Finance and an MBA from Southern Methodist University.Read Full Background




